    <RacerFolder id="1460" parentID="1057" level="2" writerID="0" creatorID="0" nodeType="1246" template="1050" sortOrder="1" createDate="2013-05-26T21:53:31" updateDate="2013-05-28T07:56:35" nodeName="Real Racers" urlName="real-racers" writerName="Rob" creatorName="Rob" path="-1,1057,1460" isDoc="">
      <bodyText><![CDATA[
<p>iRacing attracts a lot of real life racers to their service.
Some come to practice on tracks they'll soon visit and some come
just to have a good fun bit of racing. &nbsp;I've started
cataloging these racers so you can get an idea of just how
attractive this sim is to real life racers, and how well their real
life skill translates to success in the sim.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<?UMBRACO_MACRO macroAlias="RealRacersList" /> 

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>If you know any I've missed <a
href="mailto://rob.ragged@gmail.com">please email me their
details</a>, including iRacing Id, Name, series they race in, and
if possible their website/wikipedia entry.</p>
]]></bodyText>
