<p>Since the start of season 3 2012 my car has been "sponsored" by
CharmHealth, my real life employer. &nbsp;I was looking for
inspiration for a paint and colour scheme and that sprung to mind.
&nbsp;</p>

<p>But it never quite sat right with me (mainly because I have a
pic of my car as my wallpaper at work and a coworker walked past
and asked my why on Earth would I want work to sponsor me). &nbsp;I
made a new paint over the weekend and this time I used another
hobby as inspiration: weight training and power lifting. &nbsp;I
search images.google.com for some gym related logos and one of the
first ones I came across was a logo for Snap Fitness. &nbsp;Perfect
because I'm a Snap Fitness member. &nbsp;I then wanted some
supplement sponsors and Musashi was suited my colour scheme, so
they won the secondary sponsor position.</p>

<p>Anyway, here's my new paint. I think it's an improvement over
the previous. I like the red and gray swipe up the sides.
&nbsp;Looks cool. &nbsp;And notice the AIS (Australian Institute of
Sport) logo on the nose ;)</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><a href="/media/558/carrrss.png"><img src="/media/558/carrrss.png" width="700" height="301" alt="Carrrss"/></a></p>
