            <bodyText><![CDATA[
<p>Race 3 last Saturday at Suzuka and I lined up third on the grid
behind Mike Quayle in second and Scott Gray in third (no
relation!). I made a cracking start which resulted in Scott
probably turning in to me (we did collide, that's refutable but his
turning in on me was accidental - and I could't go more left
because Mike was on my inside we went 3 deep into turn 1 (mad I
know!).</p>

<p>Anyway, we got to talking briely on the forums and then via PM,
where I learnt he also lives in Brisbane, just like me. Further
talking and he lives in the suburb next me! And here we are two
random guys with the same surname (and his dad shared my name -
Robert Gray!) racing one another on a computer game, when we live
less than a kilometer away.</p>

<p>Funny!</p>
]]></bodyText>
