            <bodyText><![CDATA[
<p>First day of Spa and I set out on my Season 2 set and did a
2:17.839. &nbsp;To be fair that was with a massive tow down the
main straight at the top of the hill. &nbsp;I was setting 2:18.3's
consistently by myself, which would have still put me at the top.
None of the big boys were out though, but there were plenty of div
3 and 2 drivers.</p>

<p><a href="/media/682/spa_prac_1.PNG"><img src="/media/682/spa_prac_1.PNG" width="800" height="577" alt="Spa_prac_1"/></a></p>
]]></bodyText>
