            <teaser><![CDATA[
<p>F1Speed is a telemetry application intended to run side-by-side
with F1 2011 (and F1 2010) to display realtime data for instant
feedback on setup changes and changes to driving style, such as
braking points, throttle on points and apexes. &nbsp;It's useful
