            <bodyText><![CDATA[
<p>Why didn't someone tell me this earlier! Last season two mates
changed from the Star Mazda to the MP4/12 for Season 1 2013.
&nbsp;I kept racing the SM, getting hit by noobs.</p>

<p>I had a small go of the MP4/12C when it first came out in the
week 13, but I didn't do any formal races or practice session.
&nbsp;Now, as part of Week 13 24 hours of fun, I've had a taste for
competition and I like it. &nbsp;I was tossing up racing the car
next season anyway, but now this has made up my mind. &nbsp;The car
is much more enjoyable to drive than the V8Supercar (and apparently
a good bit faster - according to times at Interlagos). &nbsp;It
also looks fantastic.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
]]></bodyText>
            <teaser><![CDATA[
<p>My mind is made up. &nbsp;It's the McLaren next season.
&nbsp;Bring it on. and no more C class nubs!</p>
