<p><img src="/media/5548/world-of-truck-logo-552x267.jpg" alt="World of Trucks" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"/></p>

<p>I've been playing world of trucks for a while now. &nbsp;While
at first I was skeptical I'd enjoy it, I've found it to be really
great fun. &nbsp;So much so I wrote a review. &nbsp;One of my
points was how cool it would be to have multiplayer. &nbsp;Of
course, I'm not along in this desire and SCS, the makers of ETS2,
have listened and are about to release a patch to grant multiplayer
access.</p>

<blockquote>
<p>Today we would like to present you with a microscopic glimpse
into what we hinted earlier - our long standing devotion to Euro
Truck Simulator 2 evolution.</p>

<p>World of Trucks's ultimate goal is creating an environment where
you - our community - can meet, interact and compete with each
other in the expansive trucking world.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>&nbsp;It's only in Alpha but this is very promising. &nbsp;I
can't wait to get online with my mates and truck around Europe
:D</p>
]]></bodyText>
