            <bodyText><![CDATA[
<p>Inspired by the <a
href="http://www.iracing.com/bucket-list/">latest iRacing blog
post</a>, here is my real life motorsport bucket list - the
motorsport events I realistically want to see before I kick the
bucket.</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Bathurst 1000</strong> (nearly made it in 2010. &nbsp;I
had tickets and everything!) - The biggest and best touring car
race, make that sedan race, in the world. &nbsp;For closed wheel
cars, in my mind there's nothing bigger. And the atmosphere!</li>

<li><strong>Phillip Island MotoGP</strong> - Meca for the Aussie
bike fan. If only I got to see Casey Stoner work his majic around
here.</li>

<li><strong>Daytona 500</strong> (Yes, NASCAR is in this list) -
Days of Thunder. &nbsp;What an experience.</li>

<li><strong>Le Mans 24 hours</strong> - Worlds toughest endurance
event. I'd love to go with mates and spend the day just talking
cars while watching the race and there's 24 hours to do it</li>

<li><strong>British F1 Grand Prix at Silverstone</strong> - For the
environment of the F1 mad british</li>

<li><strong>Belgium F1 Grand Prix at Spa-Francorchamps</strong> -
For the track that is widely regarded as the best in the world, and
to see Eu Rogue</li>

<li><strong>Japanese F1 Grand Prix at Suzuka</strong> - For part
the track and part the crazy Japanese Fans. &nbsp;More the track
through.</li>

<li><strong>Monaco F1 Grand Prix</strong> - Oh the sound of F1 cars
around here, engine notes bouncing off the buildings.</li>

<li><strong>Indianapolis 500</strong> - The speed and tight
confines. &nbsp;I'm not so much interested in Indycar but it's a
big event</li>

<li><strong>Any European round of the WRC</strong> - Crazy guys in
close quarters. &nbsp;</li>

<li><strong>Goodwood Festival of Speed</strong> - Nothing but
petrol heads of the highest calibre here. A chance to see may
different types of cars over the years.</li>

<li><strong>A major motorshow in either Britian, France, Germany or
maybe the US.</strong></li>

<li><strong>Isle of Man TT -&nbsp;</strong> worlds most crazy bike
riders.</li>
</ul>
]]></bodyText>
